data.description: Huge Price Improvement! NEW ROOF Nov 2023! Introducing a delightful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom villa nestled within the serene community of Katherine Villas in the Village of Caroline near Sumter Landing in The Villages. This inviting property boasts a host of features that are sure to captivate your senses.   Upon entering, you'll immediately appreciate the spacious open concept design, adorned with new Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring in the main living areas and bathrooms. Natural light fills the interior, courtesy of five solar tubes strategically placed to infuse every corner with warmth and brightness.  Step into a home that is not only beautifully designed but also thoughtfully furnished. This villa comes fully equipped with stylish furnishings, including newer appliances installed in 2021, ensuring that you have all the comforts of home right at your fingertips.  For those seeking relaxation and tranquility, the highlight of this villa awaits. Imagine unwinding in your private heated spa, a haven of serenity to melt away the day's stress. Enjoy your spa time in privacy, as this villa is situated on a corner lot with no rear neighbors, creating a peaceful oasis just for you.  Safety and convenience are paramount, with hurricane shutters ensuring your peace of mind during stormy weather. Additionally, a new roof is on the horizon, ensuring the property's long-term durability and aesthetic appeal.  This villa offers the luxury of a natural gas range, adding to the convenience of your daily living. Located in close proximity to the Coconut Grove recreation facility and shopping options, you'll find entertainment and necessities just a stone's throw away.  In summary, this 2-bed, 2-bath villa in Katherine Villas is a haven of comfort and style. With its open concept design, abundant natural light, fully furnished interior, heated spa, and excellent maintenance, it's an inviting place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this private corner lot retreat your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and discover the charm of this remarkable villa in The Villages.
